POST {{logicHelperBaseUrl}}/api/validate-expense
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "employeeName": "Morgan Invalid",
  "employeeEmail": "morgan.invalid@example.com",
  "amount": 45.00,
  "category": "hardware",
  "description": "Unsupported category",
  "managerEmail": "manager.invalid@example.com"
}

### 7a. Invalid category -> Validation error on queue ingress endpoint
POST {{logicHelperBaseUrl}}/api/expense-requests
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "employeeName": "Morgan Invalid",
  "employeeEmail": "morgan.invalid@example.com",
  "amount": 45.00,
  "category": "hardware",
  "description": "Unsupported category",
  "managerEmail": "manager.invalid@example.com"
}
